{"thag16.9:0.1":"Theragatha 16.9 ","thag16.9:0.2":"Visatinipata ","thag16.9:0.3":"Pathamavagga ","thag16.9:0.4":"Anuruddhattheragatha ","thag16.9:1.1":"“Pahaya matapitaro, ","thag16.9:1.2":"bhagini natibhataro; ","thag16.9:1.3":"Panca kamagune hitva, ","thag16.9:1.4":"anuruddhova jhayati. ","thag16.9:2.1":"Sameto naccagitehi, ","thag16.9:2.2":"sammatalappabodhano; ","thag16.9:2.3":"Na tena suddhimajjhagam, ","thag16.9:2.4":"marassa visaye rato. ","thag16.9:3.1":"Etanca samatikkamma, ","thag16.9:3.2":"rato buddhassa sasane; ","thag16.9:3.3":"Sabbogham samatikkamma, ","thag16.9:3.4":"anuruddhova jhayati. ","thag16.9:4.1":"Rupa sadda rasa gandha, ","thag16.9:4.2":"photthabba ca manorama; ","thag16.9:4.3":"Ete ca samatikkamma, ","thag16.9:4.4":"anuruddhova jhayati. ","thag16.9:5.1":"Pindapatamatikkanto, ","thag16.9:5.2":"eko adutiyo muni; ","thag16.9:5.3":"Esati pamsukulani, ","thag16.9:5.4":"anuruddho anasavo. ","thag16.9:6.1":"Vicini aggahi dhovi, ","thag16.9:6.2":"rajayi dharayi muni; ","thag16.9:6.3":"Pamsukulani matima, ","thag16.9:6.4":"anuruddho anasavo. ","thag16.9:7.1":"Mahiccho ca asantuttho, ","thag16.9:7.2":"samsattho yo ca uddhato; ","thag16.9:7.3":"Tassa dhamma ime honti, ","thag16.9:7.4":"papaka sankilesika. ","thag16.9:8.1":"Sato ca hoti appiccho, ","thag16.9:8.2":"santuttho avighatava; ","thag16.9:8.3":"Pavivekarato vitto, ","thag16.9:8.4":"niccamaraddhaviriyo. ","thag16.9:9.1":"Tassa dhamma ime honti, ","thag16.9:9.2":"kusala bodhipakkhika; ","thag16.9:9.3":"Anasavo ca so hoti, ","thag16.9:9.4":"iti vuttam mahesina. ","thag16.9:10.1":"Mama sankappamannaya, ","thag16.9:10.2":"sattha loke anuttaro; ","thag16.9:10.3":"Manomayena kayena, ","thag16.9:10.4":"iddhiya upasankami. ","thag16.9:11.1":"Yada me ahu sankappo, ","thag16.9:11.2":"tato uttari desayi; ","thag16.9:11.3":"Nippapancarato buddho, ","thag16.9:11.4":"nippapancamadesayi. ","thag16.9:12.1":"Tassaham dhammamannaya, ","thag16.9:12.2":"vihasim sasane rato; ","thag16.9:12.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thag16.9:12.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thag16.9:13.1":"Pancapannasavassani, ","thag16.9:13.2":"yato nesajjiko aham; ","thag16.9:13.3":"Pancavisativassani, ","thag16.9:13.4":"yato middham samuhatam. ","thag16.9:14.1":"Nahu assasapassasa, ","thag16.9:14.2":"thitacittassa tadino; ","thag16.9:14.3":"Anejo santimarabbha, ","thag16.9:14.4":"cakkhuma parinibbuto. ","thag16.9:15.1":"Asallinena cittena, ","thag16.9:15.2":"vedanam ajjhavasayi; ","thag16.9:15.3":"Pajjotasseva nibbanam, ","thag16.9:15.4":"vimokkho cetaso ahu. ","thag16.9:16.1":"Ete pacchimaka dani, ","thag16.9:16.2":"munino phassapancama; ","thag16.9:16.3":"Nanne dhamma bhavissanti, ","thag16.9:16.4":"sambuddhe parinibbute. ","thag16.9:17.1":"Natthi dani punavaso, ","thag16.9:17.2":"devakayasmi jalini; ","thag16.9:17.3":"Vikkhino jatisamsaro, ","thag16.9:17.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","thag16.9:18.1":"Yassa muhuttena sahassadha, ","thag16.9:18.2":"Loko samvidito sabrahmakappo; ","thag16.9:18.3":"Vasi iddhigune cutupapate, ","thag16.9:18.4":"Kale passati devata sa bhikkhu. ","thag16.9:19.1":"Annabharo pure asim, ","thag16.9:19.2":"daliddo ghasaharako; ","thag16.9:19.3":"Samanam patipadesim, ","thag16.9:19.4":"uparittham yasassinam. ","thag16.9:20.1":"Somhi sakyakule jato, ","thag16.9:20.2":"anuruddhoti mam vidu; ","thag16.9:20.3":"Upeto naccagitehi, ","thag16.9:20.4":"sammatalappabodhano. ","thag16.9:21.1":"Athaddasasim sambuddham, ","thag16.9:21.2":"sattharam akutobhayam; ","thag16.9:21.3":"Tasmim cittam pasadetva, ","thag16.9:21.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","thag16.9:22.1":"Pubbenivasam janami, ","thag16.9:22.2":"yattha me vusitam pure; ","thag16.9:22.3":"Tavatimsesu devesu, ","thag16.9:22.4":"atthasim sakkajatiya. ","thag16.9:23.1":"Sattakkhattum manussindo, ","thag16.9:23.2":"aham rajjamakarayim; ","thag16.9:23.3":"Caturanto vijitavi, ","thag16.9:23.4":"jambusandassa issaro; ","thag16.9:23.5":"Adandena asatthena, ","thag16.9:23.6":"dhammena anusasayim. ","thag16.9:24.1":"Ito satta tato satta, ","thag16.9:24.2":"samsarani catuddasa; ","thag16.9:24.3":"Nivasamabhijanissam, ","thag16.9:24.4":"devaloke thito tada. ","thag16.9:25.1":"Pancangike samadhimhi, ","thag16.9:25.2":"sante ekodibhavite; ","thag16.9:25.3":"Patippassaddhiladdhamhi, ","thag16.9:25.4":"dibbacakkhu visujjhi me. ","thag16.9:26.1":"Cutupapatam janami, ","thag16.9:26.2":"sattanam agatim gatim; ","thag16.9:26.3":"Itthabhavannathabhavam, ","thag16.9:26.4":"jhane pancangike thito. ","thag16.9:27.1":"Paricinno maya sattha, ","thag16.9:27.2":"… pe ","thag16.9:27.3":"… ","thag16.9:27.4":"bhavanetti samuhata. ","thag16.9:28.1":"Vajjinam veluvagame, ","thag16.9:28.2":"aham jivitasankhaya; ","thag16.9:28.3":"Hetthato velugumbasmim, ","thag16.9:28.4":"nibbayissam anasavo”ti. ","thag16.9:28.5":"… Anuruddho thero …. "}